01:43:12,280 --> 01:43:18,200
Tak sa teraz odviažme

987
01:44:05,500 --> 01:44:06,990
Bola to skvelá šou.

988
01:44:08,500 --> 01:44:09,300
Hej?

989
01:44:11,200 --> 01:44:12,700
Mám tvoju basu.

990
01:44:13,500 --> 01:44:15,200
Zastav sa tu po ňu.

991
01:44:16,500 --> 01:44:17,400
A Riko?

992
01:44:20,000 --> 01:44:21,800
Už ju vzali na párty.

993
01:44:24,000 --> 01:44:26,800
Dobre.
Kde teraz si?

994
01:44:47,200 --> 01:44:48,400
Shun!

995
01:44:51,100 --> 01:44:52,500
Kde si, Shun?

996
01:45:15,500 --> 01:45:16,800
Tá pesnička...

997
01:45:20,800 --> 01:45:24,600
Dopekla, Shun!

998
01:45:38,700 --> 01:45:39,600
Znie to hrozne.

999
01:45:44,200 --> 01:45:46,300
Prečo ten zvuk tak vibruje?

1000
01:45:48,000 --> 01:45:49,700
Lebo má basa tenšie struny než gitara.

1001
01:46:20,200 --> 01:46:20,800
Čo?

1002
01:46:25,000 --> 01:46:26,400
Preboha.

1003
01:46:27,000 --> 01:46:28,600
Mám ti toho toľko čo povedať,

1004
01:46:29,000 --> 01:46:30,990
no neviem nájsť tie správne slová.

1005
01:46:39,100 --> 01:46:41,500
Prosím, povedz mi jedno.

1006
01:46:48,800 --> 01:46:51,300
Ogasawara-san, v tvojej hudbe

1007
01:46:52,400 --> 01:46:54,700
je tvoje pravé ja?

1008
01:47:08,000 --> 01:47:09,200
Nie je.

1009
01:47:38,000 --> 01:47:40,000
Zahráme si spolu?

1010
01:48:31,340 --> 01:48:36,720
Z ničoho nič spievam

1011
01:48:37,200 --> 01:48:41,600
Z ničoho nič ťa pobozkám

1012
01:48:41,600 --> 01:48:43,950
Mám sa ti

1013
01:48:45,000 --> 01:48:51,920
za dosť vecí ospravedlniť

1014
01:48:53,750 --> 01:48:58,580
Bojím sa, že ťa stratím

1015
01:48:59,280 --> 01:49:03,920
Po celý čas klamem

1016
01:49:03,920 --> 01:49:08,530
no pred tebou

1017
01:49:08,530 --> 01:49:15,600
chcem ukázať moje pravé ja

1018
01:49:15,600 --> 01:49:19,500
Aj keby môj život

1019
01:49:19,500 --> 01:49:26,700
vrhal tieň na tvoje svetlo

1020
01:49:27,000 --> 01:49:30,610
Dúfam, že tvoj život

1021
01:49:30,610 --> 01:49:37,200
